  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You channel your chakra into your hive as they begin to perform a symphony of buzzing. Creatures that enter the area for the first time or start their turn within the area suffer the following effects;</p><p>If an ally creature would be affected by the jutsu, they are cleansed of any Mental or Sensory conditions of rank, equal to or lower than what this jutsu was cast, and gain 4d8 temporary hit points. If the ally creature is affected by a Genjutsu, they gain advantage on their next saving throw.</p><p>If a hostile creature would be affected by the jutsu, they must make a Wisdom Saving throw. On a failed save, hostile creatures who fail the saving throw gain 2 ranks of <strong>Demoralized</strong> and must spend its entire turn exiting the radius. If the creature is unable to exit the radius they are unable to remove ranks of <strong>Demoralized</strong>.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the temporary hitpoints gained by 2d8 and the radius by 5 feet.</p>",
